The paper deals with a search problem in a geometric environment, which suggests categories such as cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.CG (Computational Geometry). The problem involves optimizing a cost function, which is a common theme in cs.RO (Robotics and Control) and cs.GT (Game Theory).
